OL,3,CTravellers warned over further Tube
OL,4,Cdisruption ahead of fresh strikes by
OL,5,Cdrivers
OL,7,FTravellers in London have been warned
OL,8,Fof disruption to Tube services next
OL,9,Fweek because of fresh strikes by
OL,10,Fdrivers.
OL,12,FMembers of the Rail, Maritime and
OL,13,FTransport union (RMT) will walk out
OL,14,Ffor 24 hours from 12 noon on Tuesday
OL,15,Fand Thursday (May 19 and 21).
OL,17,FTransport for London (TfL) said a
OL,18,Fservice is expected on most Tube lines
OL,19,Fbut warned there will be disruption to
OL,20,Fjourneys and service levels will vary
OL,21,Fthroughout the week.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/3
