OL,3,CTravellers warned over further Tube
OL,4,Cdisruption ahead of fresh strikes by
OL,5,Cdrivers
OL,7,FAfter the strikes start disruption is
OL,8,Fexpected on all Tube lines in the
OL,9,Fafternoons and services that do run
OL,10,Fwill finish early.
OL,12,FBuses, the DLR, Elizabeth line, London
OL,13,FOverground and trams will be running
OL,14,Fas normal during the industrial action
OL,15,Fbut are expected to be busy.
OL,17,FTfL advised passengers to plan ahead
OL,18,Fand allow more time for their journey.
